{{!
    @template assignfeedback_comments/summary

    Summary table of all feedback comments for a submission.

    Classes required for JS:
    * none

    Data attributes required for JS:
    * none

    Context variables required for this template:
    * comments - Array of comments containing {context, html}
    * comments[].context - A string to display the context of the comment, e.g. overall or marker
    * comments[].html - The HTML to render for the comment

    Example context (json):
    {
        "comments": [
            {
                "context": "Overall comment",
                "html": "<p>The overall comment</p>"
            },
            {
                "context": "Marker comment",
                "html": "<p>Marker one's comment</p>"
            },
            {
                "context": "Marker comment",
                "html": "<p>Marker two's comment</p>"
            }
        ]
    }
}}
<div>
    {{#comments}}
        <div>
            <strong>{{context}}</strong>
            <div>{{{html}}}</div>
            <hr>
        </div>
    {{/comments}}
</div>